---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const lastUpdated = 'July 15, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  slug="privacy"
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="CanteraPro's privacy policy: no account required, no data leaves your device, no analytics or tracking SDKs. Subscription billing is handled entirely by Apple and Google."
>
  <section class="section legal">
    <div class="container legal__inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal__updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        <strong>Draft notice:</strong> This policy is a starting draft and has not yet been
        reviewed by an attorney. Have it reviewed by a qualified professional before relying on it
        for legal compliance.
      </div>

      <h2>The short version</h2>
      <p>
        CanteraPro does not require an account, does not use the internet to function, and does
        not send your business data anywhere. Your clients, jobs, estimates, invoices, and photos
        are stored only on your own device. We don't have a server, so we don't have your data.
      </p>

      <h2>No account, no sign-up</h2>
      <p>
        CanteraPro does not ask you to create an account, provide an email address, or sign in
        with any third-party identity provider to use the app. There is no user database on our
        end, because there is no "our end" storing your information — everything lives on your
        phone.
      </p>

      <h2>No data leaves your device</h2>
      <p>
        All information you enter into CanteraPro — client contact details, job notes, photos,
        estimates, invoices, mileage, and any other business data — is stored locally on your
        device. We do not operate a cloud server that syncs, stores, or has access to this
        information. If you choose to create an encrypted backup file, that file is created,
        encrypted, and stored entirely under your control (in your device's Files app, your own
        cloud storage account, or wherever you choose to save it) — we never see it or have access
        to it.
      </p>

      <h2>No analytics or tracking SDKs</h2>
      <p>
        CanteraPro does not include third-party analytics software development kits (SDKs),
        advertising trackers, or behavioral tracking tools. We do not collect usage analytics,
        build an advertising profile of you, or sell or share your data with data brokers or
        advertisers, because we do not collect that data in the first place.
      </p>

      <h2>Subscription billing</h2>
      <p>
        If you choose to purchase a Pro subscription or a Lifetime plan, that transaction is
        processed entirely by Apple (App Store) or Google (Google Play), depending on where you
        downloaded the app. CanteraPro has no server of its own to collect, process, or store your
        payment information — Apple and Google handle billing, receipts, and payment data
        directly, under their own respective privacy policies:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple's Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Permissions the app may request</h2>
      <p>
        CanteraPro may ask for device permissions strictly to power features you choose to use —
        for example, camera access to attach job photos, or storage access to save and restore
        encrypted backup files. These permissions are used only on your device, in the moment you
        use the related feature, and are never used to transmit data off your phone.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        CanteraPro is a business tool intended for adult landscaping business owners and workers.
        It is not directed at children, and we do not knowingly collect information from
        children, consistent with the fact that we do not collect personal information from any
        user at all.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        If this policy changes, an updated version will be posted on this page with a revised
        "Last updated" date. Because the app doesn't collect contact information from you, we
        have no way to notify you directly — please check back here periodically.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Reach out at
        <a href="mailto:support@cantera-pro.com">support@cantera-pro.com</a> or visit the
        <a href={`${base}en/support/`}>Support page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
